column5: Hi all,  went fishing with a really good buddy for the first time in over a year....we had an absolute blast...we actually had tears running down our faces at times we laughed so hard.   Was windier than hell, but we put a beating on the walleye all morning and got off the lake (Lac Seul) by 1pm.   Nothing fancy, jigs and minnows in 22'FOW. I got my personal best Lac Seul walleye of just over 30".
Wow great walleye right there Simon, congrats.
Congrats on the big fish Simon
